Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.24,1:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上再说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll chat about it tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.84,1:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得别人说三哥是最幸福的王老五\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No wonder Sam's the happiest bachelor in this world
