Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.35,1:04:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了几天有没有想着我？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Did you miss me when I was away?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.59,1:04:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三哥，到了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother Sam, here we are
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.69,1:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三哥，我有点要紧的事想跟你到 写字楼去商量一下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother Sam, we've to talk privately. It's urgent
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.69,1:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如阿红先送唐先生回酒店去好不好？ 好呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hung, you check Mr Tong in at the hotel Okay!
