Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.43,1:04:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜！CECILIA\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Bye, Cecilia
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.43,1:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的有正点的介绍我？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got a special surprise for me
