Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.82,1:04:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿豹，我去了泰国两天， 有没有替我盯着阿红？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Pow, did you keep an eye on Hung when I was away
