Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.66,1:05:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豹，帮我开了它\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Pow, open it for me
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.36,1:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏陈律师机警，不然让人家剃了 眼眉也不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Luckily Chan is smart otherwise I'll be make to look a fool
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.34,1:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三哥，是我的错\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother Sam, it was my fault
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.54,1:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！没事吧？   没事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sorry. Are you alright? Yes
