Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.80,1:06:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll kill you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.91,1:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又想玩什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.72,1:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要干掉那个小子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm going to killthat bastard
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.69,1:06:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要呀！你会变成杀人凶手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, You'll become a murderer
