Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.33,1:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有他一半那么痴心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If only you were half as true to me as he is to Cecilia
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.19,1:06:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就心满意足了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then I'd be the happiest girl in the wrold
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.27,1:06:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！谁对不起三哥，我就干掉他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, I have to get kid of whoever harm Sam
