Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.38,1:07:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为我喝了这一杯酒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Drink it for me
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.98,1:07:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了你，干杯！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}For you, cheers
