Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.66,1:07:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算为了你杀人，我一样愿意\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'd sacri fice anything for you too, even my life
