Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.84,1:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三哥，我有很要紧的事要跟你说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sam, I've something very important to tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.98,1:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三爷    谢谢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Master Sam Thank you
