Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.73,1:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事情要跟你商量\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's something I want to talk to you about
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.99,1:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！我最喜欢跟你谈心事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fine, I love listening to your personal affair
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.63,1:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.60,1:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一个洋娃娃跟了我们很久啦？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This doll has been with us for quite a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.24,1:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's been 4 years
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.90,1:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旧了，不如送给别人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's getting old. Let's give it away
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.44,1:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fine!
