Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.32,1:08:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道谁是LILY？我的旧女朋友\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know Lily? My old girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.83,1:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对！是我玩腻了她\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was tired of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.69,1:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她也不应该勾引我的司机\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But she shouldn't have seduced my chauffeur
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.63,1:08:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔，出走\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}She eloped and escaped
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.83,1:08:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！我成全了她，送了她去远一点的地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I let them get far away
