Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.17,1:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿红，你说我有没有待薄过她\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hung, tell me did I ever mistreat her?
