Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.89,1:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是说有话跟我说？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You said you had something to tell me
