Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.07,1:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望不是那么重要\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I hope it's not that important
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.69,1:09:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CECILIA，我有话跟你说，是关于鸡翼的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Cecilia, it's about Chicken Wing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.19,1:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到厨房里再说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell me in in the kitchen
