Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.71,1:09:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我替你买了明天早上八点的机票 你想办法走吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got to get out of Hong Kong
