Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.02,1:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡翼呀\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Chicken
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.36,1:10:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.03,1:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是真的想我离开三哥？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are you willing to help me escape from Sam
