Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.81,1:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕死呀？   不要呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Scared of death? No!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.61,1:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没胆量！？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No guts
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.31,1:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以为阿红，什么都肯做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm ready to do anything for Hung
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.38,1:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以杀阿敏，可以杀任何人，你舔呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm willing to kill Mann or anybody. Lick it up
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.82,1:19:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.27,1:20:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿豹，搅定他！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Pow, kill them
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.23,1:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.94,1:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你死得舒服的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're not going to die that easily
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.38,1:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了我，好让我去陪阿敏\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kill me, so I can join Mann
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.03,1:20:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.16,1:20:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过找一个比阿敏更好 的女孩子给你？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I promised to find you a prettier girl
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.67,1:20:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿敏不同其他女孩子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mann was different from other girls
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.50,1:20:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿敏算是什么女孩子？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Different? Mann was cheap
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.67,1:20:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女人这么好都可以杀， 何况杀死这个贱人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm willing to kill Hung, why not Mann?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.24,1:20:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shut up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.77,1:20:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实如此，她是贱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's true, she really was a tramp
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.37,1:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连我也够胆出卖的就是贱女人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One that dares to betray me is a tramp
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.78,1:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说得对不对吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.78,1:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shut up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.08,1:20:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么你不觉得她贱格吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't believe she was a tramp
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.65,1:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.05,1:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道你反骨啦！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I knew you'd betray me!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.62,1:21:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Run her down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.36,1:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.03,1:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Quick
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.04,1:21:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点！走呀\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Quick
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.18,1:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳下去！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.06,1:22:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿红！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hung!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.79,1:23:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可以做的事暂时袛有这么多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I didn't think there's anymore I can do now
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.26,1:23:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生，我不大明白你的意思\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Doctor, I didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.23,1:24:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说病人的情况现在很不稳定\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The patient's condition is very unsteady
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.80,1:24:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她最危险的时期是明天早上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tomorrow morning is the critical period
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.83,1:24:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天早上她醒过来的话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If she pulls though by tomorrow's morning
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.37,1:24:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有机会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We still have a chance
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.80,1:24:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先出去，明天早上再来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come back tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.01,1:24:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留下来陪着她\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm staying
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.38,1:24:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生，他们本来快要结婚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Doctor, they were planning to get married
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.11,1:24:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你给他一个人情\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Please let him stay
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.52,1:24:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O.K.，出去啦！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}O.K.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.92,1:26:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应承过说不会比你早死\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You made me promise not to die before you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.26,1:26:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遵守我的诺言\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've kept my promise
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.46,1:26:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你袛给了我两个月时间，我不够的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But we've been together only 2 months, not enough
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.30,1:26:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要三十年、四十年！永远呀！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want 30 years,40years, forever, together
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.40,1:26:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有很多事没跟你做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There was so much I wanted to share with you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.24,1:26:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在甚至连你走了我都不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I wasn't aware when you died
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.04,1:27:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太不公平\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're unfair
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.92,1:27:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不公平\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Too unfair
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.59,1:27:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么开心的时候永远都是这么短\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why is happiness so fleeting
